<div class="department">
<h1>
    Specialties
</h1>

  <h2>Cardiology</h2>
  <img src="/images/img6.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="Cardiology">
      <p class="tclass">
          Welcome to the Cardiology Department at NSB Hospital, where we specialize in providing exceptional
          care for all aspects of heart health. Our dedicated team of cardiologists, nurses, and support staff 
          is committed to delivering comprehensive and personalized services to our patients. Equipped with the 
          latest technology and facilities, we offer a wide range of diagnostic, treatment, and management options 
          for various cardiac conditions, including hypertension, coronary artery disease, arrhythmias, and more. From 
          routine check-ups to complex interventions and surgeries, we strive to meet the unique needs of each individual, ensuring 
          the best possible outcomes and quality of life.
      </p>
 
      <h2>Orthopedics</h2>
      <img src="./images/img11.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="Orthopedics" >
      <p class="tclass">
        The Orthopedics Department at NSB Hospital is a beacon of expertise and compassion, offering comprehensive
         care for a wide range of musculoskeletal conditions. Led by skilled surgeons and supported by state-of-the-art
          facilities, including advanced diagnostic tools and operating theaters, the department delivers personalized 
          treatment plans tailored to each patient's needs. With a commitment to patient education, multidisciplinary collaboration,
           and ongoing research, NSB Hospital's orthopedic team ensures optimal outcomes, restoring mobility, alleviating pain, 
           and improving the quality of life for every individual in their care.Moreover, the Orthopedics Department at NSB Hospital is 
           committed to fostering a supportive and compassionate environment.  
      </p>
      
  <h2>Nephrology</h2>
  <img src="/images/img7.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="Nephrology">
      <p class="tclass">  
          Welcome to the Nephrology Department at NSB Hospital, where we are dedicated to providing exceptional 
          care for patients with kidney-related conditions. Led by a team of experienced nephrologists and supported
          by skilled nurses and allied health professionals, our department offers comprehensive services aimed at diagnosing,
          treating, and managing a wide range of kidney disorders. From chronic kidney disease and hypertension to kidney 
          stones and electrolyte imbalances, we are equipped with advanced technology and resources to deliver personalized care 
          tailored to each patient's needs. Our multidisciplinary approach ensures that patients receive comprehensive evaluations, 
          access to the latest treatment options, and ongoing support for optimal kidney health.
      </p>
 
  <h2>Radiology</h2>
  <img src="/images/img8.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="Radiology">
      <p class="tclass">  
          Welcome to the Radiology Department at NSB Hospital, where we specialize in providing advanced diagnostic imaging services. 
          Our team of radiologists and technologists utilize state-of-the-art equipment to perform a wide range of imaging studies,
          including X-rays, CT scans, MRI scans, ultrasound, and more. With a focus on accuracy and patient safety, we strive to
          deliver timely and precise diagnostic information to assist in the management of various medical conditions. Whether you
          require routine screening or specialized imaging procedures, you can trust NSB Hospital Radiology for comprehensive,
          high-quality care.In addition to our diagnostic imaging services, we also offer interventional radiology procedures
      </p>
   
  <h2>Neurology</h2>
  <img src="/images/img13.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="Neurology">
  <p class="tclass">
  Welcome to the Neurology Department at NSB Hospital, where we are dedicated to your neurological health and well-being.
  The Neurology Department at NSB Hospital is dedicated to the diagnosis and treatment of neurological disorders affecting the brain, 
  spinal cord, nerves, and muscles. Led by a team of experienced neurologists and supported by skilled healthcare professionals, we provide
  comprehensive care for conditions such as epilepsy, stroke, multiple sclerosis, Parkinson's disease, Alzheimer's disease, and neuromuscular disorders.
  Using state-of-the-art diagnostic techniques and treatment modalities, including advanced imaging and neurophysiological studies, we aim to accurately diagnose 
  neurological conditions and develop personalized treatment plans to optimize patient outcomes.
  </p>  

  <h2>ENT</h2>
  <img src="/images/img9.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="ENT">
  <p class="tclass">
    Welcome to the Ear, Nose, and Throat (ENT) Department at NSB Hospital, where we specialize in diagnosing 
    and treating disorders of the head and neck region. Our experienced ENT specialists, also known as otolaryngologists,
     provide comprehensive care for conditions such as ear infections, hearing loss, sinusitis, allergies, throat infections,
      vocal cord disorders, and more. Using advanced diagnostic techniques and treatment modalities, we aim to improve the 
    quality of life for our patients by addressing their ENT-related concerns with precision and expertise.
  </p>  

  <h2>Pulmonology</h2>
  <img src="/images/img10.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="Pulmonology">
  <p class="tclass">
    Welcome to the Pulmonology Department at NSB Hospital, where our dedicated team of pulmonologists specializes 
    in the diagnosis and treatment of various respiratory disorders. From common conditions like asthma and COPD 
    to more complex cases such as interstitial lung disease and lung cancer, we offer comprehensive care tailored 
    to each patient's needs. Using advanced diagnostic techniques and evidence-based treatments, including pulmonary 
    function tests, and personalized therapy plans, we strive to improve lung function and enhance quality of life. 
    Whether you're seeking relief from chronic cough, shortness of breath, or other respiratory symptoms, our 
    compassionate pulmonology team is committed to providing expert care and support to help you breathe easier.
  </p>  

  <h2>Gastrology</h2>
  <img src="./images/img12.png" height="125px" width="125px" alt="Gastrology" >
  <p class="tclass">
    The Gastrology Department at NSB Hospital specializes in diagnosing and treating various digestive disorders, including gastritis,
     GERD, IBD, liver diseases, and pancreatic disorders. Led by experienced gastroenterologists and equipped with advanced diagnostic 
     and therapeutic technologies, the department offers personalized care to alleviate symptoms and improve patients' digestive health and 
     overall well-being.In addition to diagnostic and therapeutic services, the Gastrology Department at NSB Hospital emphasizes patient education
      and preventive care, empowering individuals to manage their digestive health proactively and reduce the risk of recurrent issues.
  </p>
